Name: Tankex
About the game: Soldier! All to your tanks! We must win this battle at all costs! Tankex is a deathmatch game with tanks. A game can accommodate up to 8 players in 4 different teams. Compete against your friends or bots on the map. Will you be able to dominate the battlefield?! Features : ■ Choice between 3 tank skins! ■ 4 teams of 2 players! ■ A deathmatch map! ■ Multiplayer! ■ Bots ! ■ Addictive!
